{"tid":794602,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"深水埗真係唔配有高質嘅廁所","createTime":"2018-08-26T11:24:58.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-26T12:23:54.000Z","uid":167389,"like":24,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"75b633d899f48793c65c2f02021eb88064cf9598","tid":794602,"uid":167389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T11:24:58.000Z","msg":"深水埗都出名無高質嘅廁所架啦，但係發覺到就算硬件幾高質都無用，根本係人嘅問題<br />\n本身地鐵站有個職員廁所，話就話職員廁所，不過因為地鐵嘅政策所以都開比公眾用。而門口一直有人守住同埋入面有清潔工長駐打理嘅<br />\n個廁所月中裝修完，木紋裝修好似酒店咁。<br />\n本身都好期待，因為終於有個去到嘅廁所。不過用唔夠兩個禮拜就已經比人搞殘曬。<br />\n今日入去，直頭見到兩件啡色臭臭地嘅嘢係地下。係屎呀<br />\n痾尿搞到地下濕曬都算啦<br />\n點解可以連屙屎都可以屙到落地下<br />\n<br />\n我以後真係唔夠膽再去深水埗嘅公廁<br />\n亦都要同清潔工講聲辛苦曬......"},{"pid":"eda35c2a54cc5d83ceb347a965854c016ae2dd86","tid":794602,"uid":91633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T11:25:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1030d87f0ebb72337c1ca930066b382d03db8d7","tid":794602,"uid":52605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T11:26:39.000Z","msg":"啲呀伯成日等唔切瀨屎呀嘛"},{"pid":"4a22331d688916ed87a4c1a48e40a54bbdc9a57f","tid":794602,"uid":120203,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T11:28:18.000Z","msg":"真係唔明啲人點痾<br />\n成日都覺得啲人好無公德心<br />\n定覺得自己係野狗 周圍痾"},{"pid":"25a4982e681c0d590622ded87cfd8796e67cb4ce","tid":794602,"uid":55533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T11:29:02.000Z","msg":"廢老同蝗集中地<br />\n一落車成陣寒酸味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ac1a30609459e655c2e1747b30c20cfc3d2048f","tid":794602,"uid":2277,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T11:30:10.000Z","msg":"成個香港 係得深水埗d廁所係臭到急尿都唔想入去半秒"},{"pid":"09ec3a8d0674d9be5d8e8231e49bb16c1c2e6d7f","tid":794602,"uid":13474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T11:30:11.000Z","msg":"廢老南亞腥港人集中營<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9367dc9c1aecfcbd695888ad010da06746eb099","tid":794602,"uid":158613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T11:51:05.000Z","msg":"深水埗喎"},{"pid":"258bf4e323e3662928c654256c8e6412803c2211","tid":794602,"uid":23592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T12:02:06.000Z","msg":"去廁所都去得低等過人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab0c1c9be40687097d2fc8d45c0791ee0173a565","tid":794602,"uid":3309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1ac1a30609459e655c2e1747b30c20cfc3d2048f","tid":794602,"uid":2277,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T11:30:10.000Z","msg":"成個香港 係得深水埗d廁所係臭到急尿都唔想入去半秒"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T12:08:23.000Z","msg":"九龍塘站入面嗰個... 有次喺大尾督燒完嘢食返出九龍，坐坐下火車肚痛，諗住去...一入個廁格，三面牆同馬桶都係屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 屙又唔係唔屙又唔係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1244fbb68f7fa88073a1366f94b08a8de1628eb","tid":794602,"uid":38194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T12:23:54.000Z","msg":"深水埗啲人都係狗嚟㗎啦，支那狗，新移民，南亞蝗，死廢中廢老，最下賤嘅人都集中晒係呢個地方"}]}